---
import { SparklesIcon } from "@lucide/astro";
---

{/* Hero Section */}
<section class="relative pt-20 lg:pt-32 pb-16 overflow-hidden">
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full -z-10 opacity-10 pointer-events-none"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full blur-[120px]"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full blur-[120px]"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-950 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-8 border border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-900 animate-fade-in"
    >
      <SparklesIcon class="w-4 h-4" />
      <span>Nuevos tutoriales cada semana</span>
    </div>
    <h1
      class="text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black tracking-tight leading-[0.9] mb-8"
    >
      Domina la web moderna <br />
      <span
        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-indigo-600 to-violet-600 dark:from-indigo-500 dark:to-violet-500"
        >desde el núcleo</span
      >
    </h1>
    <p
      class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 leading-relaxed font-medium"
    >
      Tutoriales profundos sobre <span class="font-bold">Headless CMS</span>, <span
        class="font-bold">Stripe</span
      > y <span class="font-bold">Autenticación</span>. Eleva tus habilidades
      con el contenido de CoreX4Dev.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
      <a
        href="/blog"
        class="px-10 py-5 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-2xl font-black text-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-all shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-200 dark:shadow-indigo-900 hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        Explorar Blog
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://youtube.com/@CoreX4Dev"
        target="_blank"
        class="px-10 py-5 bg-white dark:bg-indigo-950/50 border-2 border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-900 rounded-2xl font-black text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-indigo-950/80 transition-all hover:border-slate-200 dark:hover:border-slate-800"
      >
        Ver Canal de YouTube
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
